{"tid":1050388,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蝗蟲公院晾臭腳　熱心女勸止反被打","createTime":"2019-03-07T00:59:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-07T02:22:30.000Z","uid":225464,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"9c48657deb6c810bb07f14b1dc7f1d10831d28f0","tid":1050388,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T00:59:33.000Z","msg":"<strong>惡人先告狀？大媽公院晾臭腳 熱心女勸止反被打</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2Uo5pC7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Uo5pC7&d=m7n5JD7ZMd19sx07z0x1QDsAEF7kNGMxk903cO3jeS8%3D&h=c072760e\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2Uo5pC7</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190307/photo/bkn-20190307081508740-0307_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190307081824\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190307%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190307081508740-0307_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190307081824&h=23d7d86d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n進擊的大媽？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n誰大誰惡誰正確？近日有大媽在公立醫院脫下鞋子，將腳放上座位，誰料有港媽出言勸止時，竟被惡言相向，大媽更出手打人？<br />\n<br />\n事主在Facebook發文指，周一（4日）早上陪同兒子到公院急症室求診，惟在藥劑部等待取藥期間，驚見有大媽脫下涼鞋，光着腳擱在椅子上。<br />\n<br />\n事主不禁提醒道︰「放番落嚟，唔衞生」。惟大媽深深不忿，向其破口大罵。她只好拿出手機拍片，未料大媽情緒更趨激動，「佢衝過嚟打我，繼續X我十幾分鐘，話我要畀全香港嘅男人X」。<br />\n<br />\n她大感恐怖，報警求助，可是最終因擔心兒子的病況，無暇驗傷及報案，放棄追究。她事後無奈表示︰「我哋唔可以縱容，只要惡就可以隨街打人，呢個社會慢慢會變成點？」她其後將片段公開讓網民評理。<br />\n<br />\n許多網民不忿大媽所為︰「你好勇敢，呢啲人欺善怕惡」、「唔好放過呢啲郁手郁腳嘅人」、「呢個女人都好恐怖」、「呢啲人係應該要受教訓」。"},{"pid":"c0fe17f848c8b05ace2f91d747886a363145d040","tid":1050388,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T00:59:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190307/photo/bkn-20190307081508740-0307_00822_001_02p.jpg?20190307081824\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190307%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190307081508740-0307_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20190307081824&h=7bc97145&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大媽狂罵女事主。（互聯網）"},{"pid":"342db133db412962b1f5104a67a534ccae3113bd","tid":1050388,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T00:59:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190307/photo/bkn-20190307081508740-0307_00822_001_03p.jpg?20190307081824\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190307%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190307081508740-0307_00822_001_03p.jpg%3F20190307081824&h=faec1462&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大媽情緒激動，衝向女事主動手。（互聯網）"},{"pid":"56f480957d166b818c59e99805ade9aaadb19fa5","tid":1050388,"uid":136186,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T01:01:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/7/7a/8uXq-1-.gif/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/207?cb=20130725050921\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F7%2F7a%2F8uXq-1-.gif%2Frevision%2Flatest%2Fscale-to-width-down%2F207%3Fcb%3D20130725050921&h=cf2bc565&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9c3c5a96801b528f815c474dd6f1c876a17c2820","tid":1050388,"uid":179979,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T01:04:25.000Z","msg":"老西都搵個差佬照啦"},{"pid":"f4baefbeacd47385b4d8dadbdd9896cf62f65b59","tid":1050388,"uid":57549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T01:05:33.000Z","msg":"差佬做嘢未"},{"pid":"e16bb3792037dc18a8803e896575c0434894f77f","tid":1050388,"uid":224561,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T01:07:25.000Z","msg":"呢啲情況一定要繼續引佢<br />\n佢一出手就輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d496f3b6df26ce56e50864ca49a9174c575fe20","tid":1050388,"uid":179979,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"e16bb3792037dc18a8803e896575c0434894f77f","tid":1050388,"uid":224561,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T01:07:25.000Z","msg":"呢啲情況一定要繼續引佢<br />\n佢一出手就輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj